00:46:53.520 --> 00:46:56.030
Thank you for joining me.

00:46:56.030 --> 00:46:56.040
Please

00:46:56.040 --> 00:46:58.750
like

00:46:58.750 --> 00:46:58.760
and

00:46:58.760 --> 00:47:00.630
subscribe.

00:47:02.839 --> 00:47:04.670
My wife and

00:47:04.680 --> 00:47:06.829
children appreciate

00:47:06.839 --> 00:47:08.390
your

00:47:08.400 --> 00:47:11.030
support.

00:47:19.920 --> 00:47:22.309
I'll tell you

00:47:22.319 --> 00:47:24.710
more about angel visitations

00:47:24.710 --> 00:47:24.720
later.

00:47:24.720 --> 00:47:26.430
Remember, Jesus is the Healer. I got

00:47:26.430 --> 00:47:26.440
this

00:47:26.440 --> 00:47:28.870
shirt from Nancy Dufresne—'Jesus

00:47:28.870 --> 00:47:28.880
the Healer.'He

00:47:28.880 --> 00:47:31.190
is

00:47:31.200 --> 00:47:32.990
the same yesterday, today,

00:47:33.000 --> 00:47:35.109
and forever.

00:47:43.319 --> 00:47:47.030
Keep your head up.

00:48:01.920 --> 00:48:04.870
Put a smile

00:48:04.880 --> 00:48:07.870
on your face and a song in your heart.

00:48:07.880 --> 00:48:10.309
Jesus loves you,

00:48:10.319 --> 00:48:12.510
and we will see you tomorrow.

00:48:12.520 --> 00:48:15.109
God bless you.

00:48:15.119 --> 00:48:18.079
Bye-bye.

